Jordan’s Abdullah Asks Committee to Review Charter, Petra Says

-- B y   M a s s o u d   A .   D e r h a l l y
-- 
2011-04-27T06:32:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/jordan-s-abdullah-asks-committee-to-review-charter-petra-says.html
Jordan’s  King Abdullah  asked former
Prime Minister Ahmed Lozi to chair a royal committee tasked with
reviewing the constitution and recommend amendments, the state-
run  Petra news agency  reported yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Massoud A. Derhally in  Beirut , Lebanon at   mderhally@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net . 